To install:

1) Check you have SimplePie RSS reader libraries 
   installed (libphp-simplepie under GNU/Debian)
2) Import the database from sql/pontoon.sql into your MySQL database
3) Customise html/classes/config.class
4) Copy files from html to your web root
5) Customise the backend database to your hearts content

The latest version of Pontoon can always be found at
<http://www.nth-dimension.org.uk/>.
